TopicTitle: Airport east of ksc has no biome :(

Articles.Content: I was really hoping this place would have it's own biome with comedic science reports. Sadly not. I'm sad, Jeb and I flew there last night with such high hopes.
Hmm, no but as of 0.25 (could have since changed) you could use these islands to LAND on the water biome. Separate science!
I got grasslands when i was there.
